<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="why-not">why not</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>为什么不：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Why not buy a book or some pencils?
为什么不买本书或一些铅笔呢？</p><footer>2010 北京</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>好啊：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Let’s go to the movies. 
我们去看电影吧。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Why not? 
好啊！</p></div></div>